{"tid":827712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【細心撚入】女朋友成日鬧我唔夠細心","createTime":"2018-09-19T06:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T15:38:03.000Z","uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"78a69de6dc8d257124340bcec0eae5e7a11fb048","tid":827712,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，近排女朋友成日發我脾氣，話我唔夠細心，唔識關心佢同處理佢既情緒。我認我係一個好遲鈍同粗心大意既人，成碌木咁，人地踢一腳我先識郁一郁。而且我又第一次拍拖，好多時候都唔識睇女朋友反應講野做野，搞到成日激嬲佢唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好愛我女朋友，好唔捨得同佢分開。有無細心既手足可以教下我點做個細心體貼既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知妳有上連登，如果你見到既話，我只係想話妳知我願意為妳作出任何改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5111211853091c775cefdea0391b60466b651c","tid":827712,"uid":86614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:42:48.000Z","msg":"佢有情緒病<br />\n咁鳩煩中出即飛啦"},{"pid":"8ac6eeba5cb7e3970dbe8c2134820190041e52cf","tid":827712,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c5111211853091c775cefdea0391b60466b651c","tid":827712,"uid":86614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:42:48.000Z","msg":"佢有情緒病<br />\n咁鳩煩中出即飛啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"寧教人打仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe84245a72eeae17212b0025f4c0333f200e2b3","tid":827712,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"我以前都同你一樣,但依家覺得條女好撚煩<br />\n同我一齊個時都知我係咁架啦,依家先黎呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ccd31f84d3cc392631335e44ea5f42ee6b5bd6","tid":827712,"uid":86614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"真係想解決問題<br />\n不在乎現金美食同禮物"},{"pid":"a304f7ea0f0aad1e2ce3a52a30f4fadc91004193","tid":827712,"uid":148185,"like":22,"d